About UBA Group
Our business strategy is built on being the bank of choice for businesses across the African continent. Using our extensive spread across the continent, we aim to facilitate trade and also be the pivot for the inflow of investment capital.
Learn More
UBA Pensions Custodian
UBA Pensions Custodian Limited (UBA Pensions) was incorporated in September 2005 in line with the Pension Reform Act 2004 (As Amended), and is wholly-owned subsidiary of UBA Plc. UBA Pensions is in compliance to Pensions Commission (PenCom) Corporate Governance Code.
